          "note": "Verified. `grep -ni 'lode|touchmark|ensconce|fetter|conclave|underpin|immure|augur|divine|banish' README.md` returns zero hits. Glossary entries confirmed: Enshrine README:322-323, Reliquary 325-327, Bind 339-340, Graft 343-345. The two generic 'captures' prose hits (Bind 340, Scry 431) confirmed — neither is the Lode subsystem. Lode subsystem fully absent from README."
