          "holds": true,
          "note": "Verified by reading README:534-566. Appendix enumerates Crucible Conduit, Bottle Credential Custody, Operator Federation, VPC-SC, Cosign, CDN-Aware IP Gating, Podman, Crucible-to-Crucible. No Lode kinds / capture verbs present. Cosign at 555-556: 'Deferred alongside VPC Service Controls until external distribution triggers the need.' Confirmed."
