          "note": "Verified strongly. RBSHR:67-80 reads 'Revised enshrine — universal capture verb under Lode recipe noun', kind enum 'base, tool, reliquary, wsl, podvm-wsl, podvm-native' (line 70), 'Today's mirror verb retires entirely' (line 72). `grep` of RBSHR for ensconce/fetter/conclave/underpin/immure returns zero — no per-kind verb names present. Stale frame confirmed; file is under vov_veiled/ (internal)."
